        <p class="text-lg text-muted leading-relaxed mb-4">
          <strong class="text-text-bright">lean-ctx</strong> (<em>lean context</em>) is a hybrid context optimizer —
          a transparent <strong class="text-text">shell hook</strong> with 50+ compression patterns
          (git, npm, cargo, docker, kubectl, gh, and many more),
          plus an <strong class="text-text">MCP server</strong> with 8 tools for cached reads, dependency maps,
          and entropy analysis. Includes a full <strong class="text-text">CLI</strong> with persistent stats tracking
          and one-command setup. Single Rust binary, zero dependencies.
        </p>
